======================================
neutcurve
======================================

.. image:: https://img.shields.io/pypi/v/neutcurve.svg
        :target: https://pypi.python.org/pypi/neutcurve
.. image:: https://github.com/jbloomlab/neutcurve/actions/workflows/test.yml/badge.svg
